iscuity.\", \"from\": 4942, \"to\": 5124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jolly's disjointed collection\", \"from\": 4945, \"to\": 4974}, {\"ngram\": \"scenes\", \"from\": 4978, \"to\": 4984}, {\"ngram\": \"fleeting shots\", \"from\": 4997, \"to\": 5011}, {\"ngram\": \"books\", \"from\": 5015, \"to\": 5020}, {\"ngram\": \"shelves\", \"from\": 5033, \"to\": 5040}, {\"ngram\": \"titles\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5068}, {\"ngram\": \"heterosexual adultery\", \"from\": 5079, \"to\": 5100}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual promiscuity\", \"from\": 5105, \"to\": 5123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no visual depiction of love between a man and a woman, just LGBTQIA+++ sexuality.\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5216, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no visual depiction\", \"from\": 5135, \"to\": 5154}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5162}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 5171, \"to\": 5176}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 5181, \"to\": 5188}, {\"ngram\": \"just LGBTQIA+++ sexuality\", \"from\": 5190, \"to\": 5215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Since the tableaux were showing historic moments of \\\"liberty\\\" and the victory over forces of oppression, I guess we are to assume that homosexual, bisexual and \\\"transgender\\\" people have now conquered their oppressors (Christians).\", \"from\": 5217, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5435, \"end\": 5445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999997714212702, \"rank\": 1.340249123028192e-07, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the tableaux\", \"from\": 5223, \"to\": 5235}, {\"ngram\": \"historic moments\", \"from\": 5249, \"to\": 5265}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"liberty\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"the victory\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5294}, {\"ngram\": \"forces\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5